{"id":239192,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-湖北访民许万英遭不明身份人殴打和威胁/","date":"2012-07-11T08:00:55Z","modified":"2012-07-11T08:00:55Z","title":"维权网 | 湖北访民许万英遭不明身份人殴打和威胁（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>维权网信息员关小令报道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)7<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>8<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span>, </span><span>居住在湖北省襄樊市襄城区卧龙镇潭庄村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">73</span><span>岁的访民许万英老人再次进京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>上访检举村委会主任陈文政</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>依仗政府贪官势力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>又再次雇佣凶手殴打许万英老人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>并威胁再上访就打死她。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span>因村委会主任陈文政非法将应分配给她家紧邻的宅基地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>强行霸占给他在外地居住的外甥张志江建房</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>双方产生纠纷</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>并打伤她小儿子后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>又将她小儿子谋杀身亡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>引起许万英上访</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多年无果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>但倍受政府迫害的访民许万英从不放弃为冤死儿子讨公道和保护个人合法权益的诉求</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>才招至死亡威胁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>时许，访民许万英老人正在樊城区古井巷暂住处做晚饭时，突然窜进</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>个年青人抓住她就一顿拳打脚踢，然后又揪住她头发，照脸猛抽，嘴里骂道：“叫你到处告我舅舅盖房子，老子打死你，看你还敢不敢再告。”许万英老人连呼：“杀人啦，救命啊！”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>歹徒才急忙逃跑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>随后，许万英赶紧报案，并被送进襄阳市第一人民医院诊治，右侧头皮压痛，全身多处软组织损伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span>，经襄阳市公安局樊城区分局法医学鉴定：“许万英所受损伤其程度构成轻微伤。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>打人事件已过去一个月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>因被打者许万英是一位访民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>警方没有处理结果。多年来，许万英曾多次因上访问题</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>被政府干部和公安抓捕后拘留、殴打、关黑监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>有关访民许万英举报村委会主任陈文政非法占用多处土地建房转手倒卖谋利问题，政府一直包庇不处理，关于举报陈文政非法将应批给许万英建房的宅基地，而非法给他外甥张志江霸占建房问题，直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日，才有襄樊市国土资源局作出【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>】第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">68</span><span>号行政处罚告知书：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>当事人：张志江</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>你未经批准，非法占用襄城区卧龙镇潭庄村六组</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">159.6</span><span>平方米</span><span>集体土地建住宅的行为，违反了《中华人民共和国土地管理法》第二条第三款之规定，依照《中华人民共和国土地管理法》第七十七条之规定，本机关拟对你作出如下行政处罚：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>责令退还非法占用的土地；限十五日内自行拆除非法占用土地上新建的建筑物，恢复土地原状。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>根据《中华人民共和国行政处罚法》第三十一条、第三十二条的规定，现将上述情况告知，你享有陈述、申辩的权利。如要求上述权利，请在接到本告知之日起三日内向本机关提出。逾期不提出的，视为放弃陈述和申辩权利。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>二</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span><span>七年十一月三十日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>，襄樊市国土资源局又对张志江作出【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>】第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">06</span><span>号行政处罚决定书。时间已过去近五年，处罚告知书和处罚决定书不起任何作用，只是履行形式，掩人耳目，而举报人许万英却不断受到政府和公安机关的打击迫害，如今又受到被举报人陈文政、张志江（舅甥关系）二人雇佣凶手伤害和威胁举报人生命安全的刑事案件。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-knz-JKPW-Bg/T_0rM2RqsyI/AAAAAAAAJKE/vjXZYZM8eDo/s1600/%E8%A5%84%E6%A8%8A%E8%AE%B8%E4%B8%87%E8%8B%B1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"222\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-knz-JKPW-Bg/T_0rM2RqsyI/AAAAAAAAJKE/vjXZYZM8eDo/s320/%E8%A5%84%E6%A8%8A%E8%AE%B8%E4%B8%87%E8%8B%B1.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>许万英老人</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_sSPI0Yo-Tg/T_0rkESIWKI/AAAAAAAAJKM/x6_HKK3yXVg/s1600/DSCF6011.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_sSPI0Yo-Tg/T_0rkESIWKI/AAAAAAAAJKM/x6_HKK3yXVg/s320/DSCF6011.JPG\" width=\"230\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SQD9Q6siyOE/T_0rpPEZqlI/AAAAAAAAJKU/pU5QBqhnAMI/s1600/DSCF6012.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SQD9Q6siyOE/T_0rpPEZqlI/AAAAAAAAJKU/pU5QBqhnAMI/s320/DSCF6012.JPG\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2706662432915848601?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/a4b7cb6187E88BB1.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}